Task 1: Dashboard Statistics Module

Task Name:
Dashboard Statistics and System Overview

Task Description:
Developed a dashboard module to display key performance indicators including total users, total eBooks, daily uploads, and active users, providing a real-time overview of system activity.

✅ Task 2: User Activity Monitoring Module

Task Name:
User Upload Activity Monitoring

Task Description:
Implemented a monitoring system to track and display individual user upload activities, including upload counts and usage history, enabling effective supervision of system usage.

✅ Task 3: User Role and Account Management

Task Name:
User Role and Account Management System

Task Description:
Designed and integrated a user management module to view and manage user roles, account status, and access permissions, with administrative controls for blocking, activating, and managing user accounts.

✅ Task 4: Administrative Control and Security

Task Name:
Administrative Access Control and Security Management

Task Description:
Implemented role-based access control and middleware protection to ensure that administrative features are accessible only to authorized users, enhancing system security.